headline: Is Nike (NKE) Pricing Too High After Recent 9.7% Share Price Jump?
summary: If you are wondering whether NIKE's current share price lines up with its underlying worth, this article will walk you through what the numbers are actually saying. The stock last closed at US$64.38, with a 9.7% gain over the past 30 days, a 1.7% return year to date, and longer term returns of a 9.9% decline over 1 year, a 46.5% decline over 3 years, and a 48.8% decline over 5 years.
